> "But when it comes to teaching professionals, that urgency is lagging."

See the [House Bill H.R.2544 - Teacher Health and Wellness Act](https://www.congress.gov/bill/115th-congress/house-bill/2544/text 
): In 2017, a bill was introduced in the House of Representatives calling for funding to support a five-year study of teacher stress and the impact it has on teacher retention. The bill has remained stagnant since May of 2017.
